SUMMARY:🥗 Lunch: Breakfast Burrito (leftover)
DESCRIPTION:Recipe: Breakfast Burrito\n(Leftover - no cooking needed!)\nServings: 2\nPrep: 5 min | Cook: 10 min | Total: 15 min\n\nTip: Meal prep: wrap in foil and freeze. Reheat in microwave 2-3 min.
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:mealplan-20260720-dinner-3@mealplanner
